---
// Beautiful, modern, and accomplished HerWAY Forward Project Showcase
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>HerWAY Forward Project | Completed Impact & Showcase</title>
		<meta name="description" content="An impact showcase of the HerWAY Forward Project, which empowered first-time teenage mothers in Gasabo District, Rwanda to reclaim their education." />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,800;1,400&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;0,800;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#FFFDF9] via-[#F4F9F4] to-[#F1F7FC] text-slate-800 font-sans antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col selection:bg-amber-100">
		
		<!-- Custom Navigation Bar -->
		<header class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-emerald-50/50 py-5 sticky top-0 z-50">
			<nav class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
					<div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-400 via-emerald-500 to-sky-400 flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner">
						<span class="text-white font-extrabold text-sm tracking-tighter">HWF</span>
					</div>
					<span class="font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-800 to-sky-800 tracking-tight text-lg">HerWAY Forward Project</span>
				</div>
				<div class="space-x-6 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-800">
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Home</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
		</header>
		
		<main class="flex-grow max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 w-full">
			
			<!-- Hero Section - Celebrating Accomplished Peace Work -->
			<section class="relative mb-20 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50/60 via-emerald-50/40 to-sky-50/50 border border-amber-100/40 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-40 h-40 bg-amber-200/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				<div class="absolute -left-10 -bottom-10 w-40 h-40 bg-sky-200/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				
				<div class="relative space-y-6 max-w-3xl">
					<div class="inline-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-amber-800 bg-amber-100/80 px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm">
							Completed Davis Projects for Peace Project
						</span>
						<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-emerald-800 bg-emerald-100/80 px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm">
							Gasabo District, Rwanda
						</span>
					</div>
					
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 leading-none font-serif">
						Reclaiming Dreams. <br />
						<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 via-amber-500 to-sky-500">Moving HerWAY Forward.</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
						A look back at how we empowered first-time teenage mothers (ages 15–19) in Rwanda to reclaim their education, master vital life skills, and build self-determined, independent futures.
					</p>

					<div class="pt-4 flex items-center space-x-3 text-sm text-slate-500">
						<div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs shadow-sm">SU</div>
						<span>Led by <strong class="text-slate-800 font-semibold">Sandrine Uwantege</strong> | Washington and Lee University</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Mission & Vision Accomplished Cards -->
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
				<div class="relative bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-900 to-emerald-850 text-emerald-50 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-md overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
					<div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 w-24 h-24 bg-emerald-750 rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50"></div>
					<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-300 mb-3">The Mission We Delivered</h3>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
						We successfully empowered first-time teenage mothers in Rwanda to reclaim their education, realize their potential, and build confident, independent futures through personalized planning and communities of support[cite: 1].
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="relative bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-600 to-amber-500 text-amber-50 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-md overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
					<div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 w-24 h-24 bg-amber-455 rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50"></div>
					<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-100 mb-3">Our Lasting Vision</h3>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
						To build a Rwanda where early pregnancy no longer ends a young woman's dreams, and where every teenage mother is met with a pathway to education, health, and financial independence[cite: 1].
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Completed Activities Section -->
			<section class="mb-20">
				<div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 space-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 font-serif">Activities Completed</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-500">The core pillars of our project execution in Rwanda[cite: 1].</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<!-- Activity 1 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-center relative">
							<span class="text-emerald-800 font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide uppercase">The IEP Roadmaps</span>
							<div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-emerald-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">Step 01</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 flex-grow space-y-3">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg">Individualized Empowerment Plans</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								Every participant partnered with a mentor to design her own personalized roadmap[cite: 1]. Together, they assessed educational backgrounds and interests to decide the best individual paths forward[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Activity 2 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-amber-50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-100 to-orange-50 flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-center relative">
							<span class="text-amber-800 font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide uppercase">Skills & Motivation</span>
							<div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-amber-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">Step 02</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 flex-grow space-y-3">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg">Vocational & Inspiration Workshops</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								We hosted tailoring workshops and practical skills sessions[cite: 1]. We invited inspirational guest speakers—former teenage mothers who built successful lives—to motivate and build self-sufficiency[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Activity 3 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-sky-50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-100 to-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-center relative">
							<span class="text-sky-800 font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide uppercase">Health & Saving</span>
							<div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-sky-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">Step 03</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 flex-grow space-y-3">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg">SRHR & Financial Literacy</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								Participants completed age-appropriate reproductive health education to protect their bodies[cite: 1]. They also learned to budget, save, and formed peer-led saving groups to build collaborative financial independence[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Photo Showcase (Optimized for real photos of your accomplishments!) -->
			<section class="mb-20 bg-emerald-950 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
				<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(#fff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_1px]"></div>
				<div class="max-w-xl space-y-6 relative">
					<span class="text-xs font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-300 font-sans">Project Impact Gallery</span>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold font-serif">Moments from Gasabo District</h2>
					<p class="text-emerald-100/80 leading-relaxed font-light">
						A look into our weekly sessions, workshops, and peer meetings[cite: 1]. Replace these placeholders with your actual photos by adding them to the <code class="bg-emerald-900/60 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-200 text-xs">public/images/</code> folder!
					</p>
					
					<!-- Gallery Grid -->
					<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-4">
						<div class="h-40 rounded-xl bg-emerald-900/50 border border-emerald-800/40 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-emerald-300/60 font-medium">
							<!-- <img src="/images/your-workshop-photo.jpg" alt="Workshop Session" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /> -->
							[ Workshop Session Photo ]
						</div>
						<div class="h-40 rounded-xl bg-emerald-900/50 border border-emerald-800/40 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-emerald-300/60 font-medium">
							<!-- <img src="/images/your-mentorship-photo.jpg" alt="Mentorship Session" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /> -->
							[ Peer Mentorship Session Photo ]
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Impact & Metrics Showcase -->
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-20 border-t border-emerald-100/50 pt-16">
				<div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 font-serif">Project Outcomes</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Our community-centered model produced direct, life-changing results for first-time teenage mothers[cite: 1].</p>
				</div>
				<div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
						<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-50 text-center space-y-1">
							<div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-emerald-600">20</div>
							<div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-450">Young Mothers Empowered[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-50 text-center space-y-1">
							<div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-amber-600">10</div>
							<div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-450">Dedicated Mentors[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-sky-50 text-center space-y-1">
							<div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-sky-600">100%</div>
							<div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-450">Actionable IEP Plans[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-slate-150/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/30 space-y-3">
						<h4 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Lasting Accomplishments</h4>
						<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="text-emerald-600">✔</span> **Educational Clarity**: Defined plans to rejoin formal school or begin professional trades[cite: 1].
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="text-emerald-600">✔</span> **Informed Health**: Improved reproductive rights literacy, lowering repeat pregnancy risks[cite: 1].
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="text-emerald-600">✔</span> **Financial Independence**: Savings habits fostered through ongoing peer savings circles[cite: 1].
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="text-emerald-600">✔</span> **Stigma Reduced**: Emotional isolation replaced with a thriving, permanent peer support network[cite: 1].
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</main>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<footer class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-12 text-center space-y-4">
			<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-2">
				<div class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-amber-400">
					HerWAY Forward Project
				</div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
					Reclaiming dreams. Building confidence. Transforming futures. A community-supported project for teenage mothers in Gasabo District, Rwanda[cite: 1].
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-800 pt-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} HerWAY Forward Project. Supported by the Davis Projects for Peace Fellowship[cite: 1].
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>